Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:51.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}and I’m alright
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.64,0:22:53.01,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I’ll be alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:54.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}yeah I hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.72,0:22:56.27,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I care about you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:23:01.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}伸びた髪を風がからかってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}全部意味があるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:07.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}立ち止まった日々も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:13.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今さらわかってあなたに追いついたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:17.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ほら　この目じゃなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:25.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}見えなかったものが　どうして　溢れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:31.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}せめて　会いたいよなんて言わないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:36.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ねえ　今日だけは思い出していいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:43.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}だからあなたとまた巡りあったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:48.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}もう迷わない今を選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.99,0:23:52.20,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Anytime anywhere yah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:54.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どこにいても
Dialogue: 1,0:23:55.45,0:23:57.58,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Anytime anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:57.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑ってみせて
Dialogue: 1,0:24:00.08,0:24:01.87,EDJP - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I’ll be there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:24:00.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}目を閉じれば　いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:03.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}絶対なんてなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:06.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつでも届いているから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:09.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}その涙だって大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}きっと夜が明けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:19.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I’m whispering our lullaby for you to come back home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:51.97,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我还好
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.64,0:22:53.01,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:54.97,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我听到了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.72,0:22:56.27,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:23:01.65,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}轻风在长发间嬉戏着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.94,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}这一切都有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:07.24,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}包括那些驻足不前的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:13.33,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}到如今我也终于能理解并追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:17.62,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}如果不是这双眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:25.05,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}那么这么多看不到的事物 又如何满溢出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:31.30,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}至少 我不会说出想见到你这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:36.97,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我说 只有今天让我追忆你可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:43.02,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}所以 如果我们能再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:48.94,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我一定不再会迷茫 而是选择当下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:54.74,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.99,0:23:52.20,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}随时 随地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:57.58,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我都会为你欢笑
Dialogue: 1,0:23:55.45,0:23:57.58,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}随时 随地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:24:00.58,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}每当合上双眼 总是
Dialogue: 1,0:24:00.08,0:24:01.87,EDCH - 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:03.42,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就算没有绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:06.38,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也总能够传达到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:09.59,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就算落泪也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.88,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因为黎明一定会来临
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:19.14,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我会为你的归来轻声歌唱着我们摇篮曲
